        {
            "title": "安永料本港今年新股集資額達2800億元　重奪全球首位",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">安永預期，本港今年新股市場集資額達2800億元，按年大增2.18倍，是近5年以來第二高，融資規模由去年全球排名第四，升至全球首位。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"巴士的報記者攝\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/09/20250917_FI_source-web_00388-2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"巴士的報記者攝\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/09/20250917_FI_source-web_00388-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">巴士的報記者攝</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">預計今年全年有過百隻新股上市，較去年增長43%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">安永發表報告指出，香港今年首十大IPO合計集資1547億元，佔全年總額逾半，平均融資規模按年增長1.37倍，其中8隻新股集資額超過100億元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">安永提到，港交所於今年8月4日正式實施IPO定價及分配新規，引入回撥比例上限提升至35%，及公開認購比例鎖定機制，新規落地後，36隻新股中僅有6宗跌穿招股價。今年以來新股首日平均回報率達38%，創近5年新高，首日破發率則降至24%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">另外，內地A股新股市場在穩監管與優化結構背景下實現溫和增長，全年預計逾百家企業首發上市，集資規模突破1100億元人民幣，按年增長超過53%。預計上海及深圳證券交易所全年集資規模，分別全球排名第五和第八。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15461710-%e5%ae%89%e6%b0%b8%e6%96%99%e6%9c%ac%e6%b8%af%e4%bb%8a%e5%b9%b4%e6%96%b0%e8%82%a1%e9%9b%86%e8%b3%87%e9%a1%8d%e9%81%942800%e5%84%84%e5%85%83%e3%80%80%e9%87%8d%e5%a5%aa%e5%85%a8%e7%90%83%e9%a6%96-2",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/20250203_FI_source-web_00388-1.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-11-27 15:45:31",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "先升後回 滬指收升11點 深指轉跌0.25% 萬科A成表現最差A+H股份",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">內地A股午市先升後回順，深市股指更倒跌收場。萬科(02202)A股(000002.SZ)表現，在A+H企業中敬陪末座。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"萬科2022年度年報封面\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/07/02202.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"萬科2022年度年報封面\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/07/02202.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">萬科2022年度年報封面</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">上證綜指早市初段略為反覆，曾短暫倒跌，但低位3864點時僅跌不足1點，未幾已回歸升勢，約上午10時前後升幅已擴大至約25點，午後一度衝上3895點，漲31點，其後升幅反覆收窄；滬指最後收報3875點，升幅收窄至11點或0.29%，成交6985.19億元(人民幣‧下同)。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">深證成指今早稍微低開後亦迅速轉升，於上午約10時曾重越萬三點關口，最高見13082點，升174點，其後進入下降軌，午市尾段更開始倒跌；深指收報12875點，跌32點或0.25%，成交1.01萬億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滬深300指數也跌2點或0.05%，以4515點收市；創業板指數跌13點或0.44%，報3031點。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240307_FI_source-ap_AShare-11.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240307_FI_source-ap_AShare-11.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">萬科多隻境內債連日急跌，今早已有6隻債券跌逾30%被深交所實施臨時停牌，公司A股亦全日「潛水」，收報5.47元，跌7.13%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">個別於深市掛牌的重磅股亦受壓，滬電股份(002463.SZ)挫3.71%，立訊精密(002475.SZ)跌1.11%；三花智控(02050)A股(002050.SZ)跌0.93%，報42.79元；寧德時代(03750)A股(300750.SZ)跌0.44%，報371.2元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">今早強勢的芯片板塊，部份亦於午後明顯轉弱。寒武紀(688256.SH)曾倒跌，收報1317.36元，微升0.21%；中芯國際(00981)A股(688981.SH)升幅收窄至0.01%，報99.13元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15461597-%e5%85%88%e5%8d%87%e5%be%8c%e5%9b%9e-%e6%bb%ac%e6%8c%87%e6%94%b6%e5%8d%8711%e9%bb%9e-%e6%b7%b1%e6%8c%87%e8%bd%89%e8%b7%8c0-25-%e8%90%ac%e7%a7%91a%e6%88%90%e8%a1%a8%e7%8f%be%e6%9c%80%e5%b7%aeah",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250408_FI_source-ap_China-2.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-11-27 15:10:30",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
