            "title": "港股午市中段轉弱 稍早前曾倒跌",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">港股午市先揚後回吐，於下午3時前曾倒跌，暫微升不足10點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">阿里巴巴(09988)跌幅擴大至約2.6%，騰訊(00700)亦跌約1.5%。小米(01810)升幅收窄至約2.8%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15461556-%e6%b8%af%e8%82%a1%e5%8d%88%e5%b8%82%e4%b8%ad%e6%ae%b5%e8%bd%89%e5%bc%b1-%e7%a8%8d%e6%97%a9%e5%89%8d%e5%80%92%e8%b7%8c",
